1
- send sscrt to treasury
- treasury sends A (allocation) to scrt-staking
- scrt-staking redeems all for scrt and stakes

2
- treasury claims rewards
- scrt-staking withdraws rewards to self
- scrt-staking redeems all for sscrt
- scrt-staking sends all sscrt to treasury
    -- this would trigger 1 and redelegate A

3
- treasury unbonds
- scrt-staking undelegates to self
- scrt-staking redeems all for sscrt
- scrt-staking sends all sscrt to treasury
    -- this would trigger 1 and redelegate A
